  "headline": "Philosophy of Mind",
  "description": "Philosophy of mind examines the nature of consciousness, mental states, and the mind-body relationship. Positions: dualism (Descartes: mind and body separate), physicalism (mind = brain), functionalism (mental states = functional roles), panpsychism (consciousness is fundamental). The 'hard problem' (Chalmers): why does physical processing produce subjective experience?",
